  "title": "Kidding Around",
  "description": "Get ready for an all-ages improv spectacle! Rapid Fire creates every show with your ideas. It's an open-door performance perfect for families; the lobby's open for breaks, snacks, or AC. See positivity, listening, and teamwork shine. The show for kids at Fringe!",
  "credits": "<strong>Director</strong>: Joleen Ballendine<br/><strong>Cast</strong>: Rapid Fire Theatre Ensemble &amp; Guests<br/>",
  "website": "https://rapidfiretheatre.com",
  "plain_language": "Hey kids! This is a fun show made just for you. The silly actors from Rapid Fire Theatre make everything up as they go. They don’t have a script, so they need your help! You can shout out ideas and even talk to the actors (if you want). That means the show is different every time! It’s funny, silly, and full of laughs. Come join the fun!",
